OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely
OL,6,Fclear skies at first, although a brief
OL,7,Fisolated thundery shower may affect
OL,8,Feastern areas this evening. Cloud
OL,9,Fincreasing from the west, extending to
OL,10,Fall parts by the morning. However, it
OL,11,Fshould remain generally dry. Winds
OL,12,Fmainly light.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FRather cloudy at first but
OL,15,Fsunny spells spells developing through
OL,16,Fthe day. Winds generally light, with
OL,17,Ftemperatures slightly lower than
OL,18,FFriday, but still very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
